Slant height........
a^2 + b^2 = l^2
30^2 + 40^2 = l^2
900 + 1600 = l^2
2500 = l^2
50 = l

Lateral area........
L = πrl
L = π(30)(50)
L = 1500π

Base area...........
B = πr^2
B = π(30^2)
B = 900π

Total surface area..
S = L + B
S = 1500π + 900π
S = 2400π
S = 7536

